.checkbox {
	display: inline-flex;
	vertical-align: text-bottom;
	width: 16;
	height: 16;
	background-size: 16px;
	margin-left: 2px;
	margin-right: 5px;
}

.checkbox-on {
	background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg%20width%3D%2216%22%20height%3D%2216%22%20viewBox%3D%220%200%2016%2016%22%20fill%3D%22none%22%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%3E%0A%3Crect%20width%3D%2216%22%20height%3D%2216%22%20fill%3D%22%2358A9D7%22%2F%3E%0A%3Cpath%20d%3D%22M6.71429%2012.2852L14%204.9995L12.7143%203.71436L6.71429%209.71378L3.28571%206.2831L2%207.57092L6.71429%2012.2852Z%22%20fill%3D%22white%22%2F%3E%0A%3C%2Fsvg%3E");
}

.checkbox-off {
	background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml;charset=UTF-8,%3Csvg%20width%3D%2216%22%20height%3D%2216%22%20viewBox%3D%220%200%2016%2016%22%20fill%3D%22none%22%20xmlns%3D%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2F2000%2Fsvg%22%3E%0A%3Crect%20x%3D%220.75%22%20y%3D%220.75%22%20width%3D%2214.5%22%20height%3D%2214.5%22%20fill%3D%22white%22%20stroke%3D%22%2336352F%22%20stroke-width%3D%221.5%22%2F%3E%0A%3C%2Fsvg%3E");
}
	
</style></head><body><article id="2697a5d8-3064-80b9-9acb-f2b2eea2d749" class="page sans"><header><h1 class="page-title" dir="auto">진행과정</h1><p class="page-description" dir="auto"></p></header><div class="page-body"><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><h1 id="2697a5d8-3064-804e-aed7-f075b239561f" class="">📊 아동 콘텐츠 데이터 분석 &amp; 생성형 AI 활용 정리</h1></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><h2 id="2697a5d8-3064-80c5-9c66-ede96fd40b11" class="">1. 🎥 데이터 수집 (YouTube API 기반)</h2></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-80bb-8e71-c0586c0651d3" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc"><strong>채널 선택</strong><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-8015-820f-dc559e117828" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">Sesame Street, Super Simple Songs, PBS Kids, Little Baby Bum, Mother Goose Club, Blippi 등</li></ul></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-80b4-b904-eb79d4e15d96" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc"><strong>영상 메타데이터 수집</strong><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-803b-898e-d4de39f8307a" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">유튜브 Data API + <code>yt_dlp</code> 활용</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-80ed-84f5-f6646e865fe8" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle"><code>videos.csv</code> 저장 (video_id, title, channel, view, like 등)</li></ul></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-80bc-a08a-ed26600625e1" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc"><strong>자막/오디오 다운로드</strong><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-80ab-a229-f56dbfb4e6f2" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">yt-dlp로 자동 자막(.vtt) 추출</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-801a-acd7-d68786fb6438" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">오디오 <code>.wav</code> 추출 (음악/가사 분석용)</li></ul></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><hr id="2697a5d8-3064-80eb-9758-cf5ffc2f7f40"/></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><h2 id="2697a5d8-3064-806c-b4a4-e0bc390b8e2e" class="">2. 📝 텍스트(가사) 분석</h2></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-8047-b772-d21594fd284c" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc"><strong>STT(음성→텍스트 변환)</strong><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-8075-8255-fd012d8180fe" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle"><code>faster-whisper</code> (Whisper 기반 경량화 STT)</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-80a3-8b76-d4c69f2a420e" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">모든 오디오 → 자막/가사 추출 (<code>text_ngrams.csv</code>)</li></ul></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-8047-a40a-c4a71f37727f" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc"><strong>반복성 분석</strong><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-80d2-85e9-cc956635c9e1" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle"><code>caption_repeats.py</code></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-8076-9401-f2d17ffc601a" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">특정 단어나 구절이 반복되는 정도 산출</li></ul></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-802d-a319-d369acb3f684" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc"><strong>언어 패턴</strong><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-805b-8ff8-f0ab7e919cfb" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">N-gram(uni/bi/tri) 분석</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-80e0-9ed7-e42cd1b95a67" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">WordCloud 생성 → 상위 단어: <em>baby, dance, head, love, night...</em></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-8005-a2e2-ef937bb55607" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">Mood별 단어 히트맵: Excited=활동, Calm=자장가, Playful=가족/사랑</li></ul></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><hr id="2697a5d8-3064-80cc-a063-f055a1f8d9a5"/></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><h2 id="2697a5d8-3064-80fc-93ea-ed4c3d1c061d" class="">3. 🎶 오디오 분석</h2></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-801d-918f-db2aaa56e1e9" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc"><strong>리듬/반복성</strong><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-802b-b3a1-e996183a5841" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle"><code>audio_repeat_score.py</code> → <code>audio_features.csv</code></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-8085-81c7-cdd541a94c4a" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">추출 지표: repeat_score, bpm_est, dominant_period, mood</li></ul></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-80f9-a786-dac2f0979cda" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc"><strong>멜로디/음역/조성</strong><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-8092-862a-ed0dafcf1aaa" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle"><code>melody_key_batch.py</code> → <code>melody_key_features.csv</code></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-809d-b0b5-d847b603e171" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">추출 지표: median_f0_hz, pitch_range_semitones, key(C major 등), voiced_ratio</li></ul></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-8032-a045-f1f445ccf95b" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc"><strong>최종 통합</strong><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-8047-b732-dcc226ca5a4a" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle"><code>audio_full_features.csv</code> (repeat_score + bpm + mood + key + 음역대)</li></ul></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><hr id="2697a5d8-3064-8084-821f-e47db5c5e30a"/></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><h2 id="2697a5d8-3064-800c-a868-d738a415ebf0" class="">4. 📈 시각화 &amp; 인사이트</h2></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-8045-8329-ef14a9dfc460" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc"><strong>Mood 분포</strong>: Playful/Excited 곡이 대부분 → 밝은 톤 선호</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-8018-b3ae-cd2bb8e7bfc4" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc"><strong>Repeat vs BPM</strong>: BPM 100<del>140, repeat_score 0.2</del>0.4 → 일정한 반복 + 중간 템포</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-808c-8e20-e3c38636a4d6" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc"><strong>채널별 반복성</strong>: 교육 중심 채널일수록 반복성 ↑</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-800b-a3b3-d8b55d3db72f" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc"><strong>WordCloud &amp; 히트맵</strong>: 단어군별 차이 → Excited=행동, Calm=자장가, Playful=가족</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-8057-8c98-c6b3df201641" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc"><strong>Pitch range</strong>: 대체로 1옥타브 이내</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-8052-9f52-da363fecec8b" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc"><strong>Key 분포</strong>: 메이저 키 위주 (C/G major) → 밝고 친근한 느낌</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><hr id="2697a5d8-3064-803b-85cf-e7e15084fcc4"/></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><h2 id="2697a5d8-3064-8034-9079-e06bf65e468d" class="">5. 🤖 생성형 AI 활용 가이드라인</h2></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-8096-ba40-e0896e2b9b10" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc"><strong>음악(멜로디)</strong><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-8020-8ade-d14b64ea9178" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">조건: BPM 100~140, C major, pitch range ≤ 12 semitones, 반복 패턴 포함</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-8062-ae9a-dbbc07d2d456" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">프롬프트 예시:<div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/prism.min.js" integrity="sha512-7Z9J3l1+EYfeaPKcGXu3MS/7T+w19WtKQY/n+xzmw4hZhJ9tyYmcUS+4QqAlzhicE5LAfMQSF3iFTK9bQdTxXg==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerPolicy="no-referrer"></script><link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/themes/prism.min.css" integrity="sha512-tN7Ec6zAFaVSG3TpNAKtk4DOHNpSwKHxxrsiw4GHKESGPs5njn/0sMCUMl2svV4wo4BK/rCP7juYz+zx+l6oeQ==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerPolicy="no-referrer"/><pre id="2697a5d8-3064-80e8-8bda-fdfeb33b77c9" class="code code-wrap"><code class="language-Plain Text" style="white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all">Create a children&#x27;s song melody in C major, 120 BPM.
The melody should stay within one octave (C4 to G5),
with repeating motifs and playful mood.

</code></pre></div></li></ul></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-80b0-9923-c7ea4cf3a7b3" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc"><strong>가사(텍스트)</strong><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-800b-a75e-c6308b86bbd8" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">조건: 짧고 반복적, 핵심 단어(동물, 가족, 신체, 행동) 포함</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-807f-b161-ffe6336807f9" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">프롬프트 예시:<div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/prism.min.js" integrity="sha512-7Z9J3l1+EYfeaPKcGXu3MS/7T+w19WtKQY/n+xzmw4hZhJ9tyYmcUS+4QqAlzhicE5LAfMQSF3iFTK9bQdTxXg==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerPolicy="no-referrer"></script><link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/themes/prism.min.css" integrity="sha512-tN7Ec6zAFaVSG3TpNAKtk4DOHNpSwKHxxrsiw4GHKESGPs5njn/0sMCUMl2svV4wo4BK/rCP7juYz+zx+l6oeQ==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerPolicy="no-referrer"/><pre id="2697a5d8-3064-8006-8c22-c702b5faf9e2" class="code code-wrap"><code class="language-Plain Text" style="white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all">Write Korean children&#x27;s lyrics using body parts.
Repeat words like &#x27;머리, 어깨, 무릎, 발&#x27; in a playful mood.

</code></pre></div></li></ul></div></li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-806c-a369-f5e3b65f74ba" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:disc"><strong>캐릭터/비주얼</strong><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-806c-b28f-d0e543677c46" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">조건: 귀여운 동물·친숙한 대상, 밝은 색상, 단순한 형태</li></ul></div><div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><ul id="2697a5d8-3064-805e-9462-e92bb98479da" class="bulleted-list"><li style="list-style-type:circle">프롬프트 예시:<div style="display:contents" dir="auto"><script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/prism.min.js" integrity="sha512-7Z9J3l1+EYfeaPKcGXu3MS/7T+w19WtKQY/n+xzmw4hZhJ9tyYmcUS+4QqAlzhicE5LAfMQSF3iFTK9bQdTxXg==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerPolicy="no-referrer"></script><link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/themes/prism.min.css" integrity="sha512-tN7Ec6zAFaVSG3TpNAKtk4DOHNpSwKHxxrsiw4GHKESGPs5njn/0sMCUMl2svV4wo4BK/rCP7juYz+zx+l6oeQ==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerPolicy="no-referrer"/><pre id="2697a5d8-3064-801b-8d7d-f74af30aecd4" class="code code-wrap"><code class="language-Plain Text" style="white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-all">Design a cute character holding Korean Hangul letters.
Style: bright colors, round shapes, child-friendly.

</code></pre></div></li></ul></div></li></ul></div></div></article><span class="sans" style="font-size:14px;padding-top:2em"></span></body></html>